    "comment_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "The issue is due to the fact the LSP changes the prefix, by changing the `.` to `->`, which now causes the match to fail.\n\nIdeally, the match should not include the trigger characters, but I am not sure how \"easy\" would be to just ignore them as they are integral part of the LSP response.",
